&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;PART TIME MEDICAL RECEPTIONIST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a part time medical receptionist to work in a busy NHS GP Surgery in Greenwich, 20 hours per week 5 days a week. Applicants must be willing to work flexible hours and to cover staff holidays.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for candidates who are professional, friendly, have a good telephone manner and take pride in their work. You will be the first point of contact for the patients in our surgery and need to make a good lasting impression. You must have excellent computer skills. Full training will be provided on our Vision clinical system&lt;/p&gt;
